beer.beer_description: Our eagerly anticipated 2024 edition of the Freshest Haze IPA. We've used freshly harvested Galaxy hops, plucked at the peak of ripeness and infused into the brew within days. Brewed only once a year during harvest, this limited-edition release has become a tradition since 2019. With low bitterness and a profile that perfectly balances hoppy notes with juicy fruitiness, Freshest Haze is a testament to the resinous fresh hop style.
